{"version":3,"kind":"Article","sha256":"14b1ecf6643cf3e1ff70a31e11f36b3db431a06b9b81f129d22729ac11cf0475","slug":"consult","location":"/profile/delib/default/consult.md","dependencies":[],"frontmatter":{"title":"议题：内部咨询制度","content_includes_title":false,"github":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech","keywords":["quanttide","documentation"],"numbering":{"title":{"offset":3}},"source_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/blob/main/docs/profile/delib/default/consult.md","edit_url":"https://github.com/quanttide/quanttide-tech/edit/main/docs/profile/delib/default/consult.md","exports":[{"format":"md","filename":"consult.md","url":"/consult-dd18ece5316865bbc6c36cc53270667b.md"}]},"mdast":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"block","children":[{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"之前确立的有事向创始人走咨询流程的制度并没有实际的落实。从我的实验情况来看，主要是大家不知道什么时候该走以及怎么走。因此，我们反向的来做这个事情，由创始人向各个部门去咨询专业问题，通过这种方式来打磨这个咨询流程。","position":{"start":{"line":3,"column":1},"end":{"line":3,"column":1}},"key":"VwxhVHxsYb"}],"key":"dJ698OfzCB"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"嗯，它和培训制度的主要区别是，培训制度是老带新，是传授已有经验。咨询流程的主要目的是为了解决不知道的新问题，然后并且这些新问题有较大的影响范围，需要持续关注。如果一次性解决不了的话，还要继续去解决。这样子，通过培训流程去容纳这个容器有两个目的，一个目的是，把困困影响较大的困难统一装在这个容器里面，可以持续地解决。嗯，持续的观察，就是我们需要知道真正的困难都有哪些。","position":{"start":{"line":5,"column":1},"end":{"line":5,"column":1}},"key":"N3NqVo11it"}],"key":"gS94NUGVtt"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"已经解决的问题就可以变成手册的等素材，如果没有解决的话，就可以变成新媒体的素材，嗯，在小红书的平台上公开去问嗯，根据之前前的实验，这一类的咨询帖是可以获得流量和关注的。","position":{"start":{"line":7,"column":1},"end":{"line":7,"column":1}},"key":"EilQO8ZEc9"}],"key":"wBufPqlmOT"}],"key":"sZiuzCIizo"}],"key":"w3J3E1N4F7"},"references":{"cite":{"order":[],"data":{}}}}